node.text:
How do I do it all?? Truth be told…I don’t😂

✨That being said, I do have tips and tools to stay on top of what I have going on. 

✨Today on the Basics of Bossing Up, I’m going to tell you all about why a notebook (yes, that’s right, a pen and paper in 2021) helps me get it done!

✨Watch the full episode to learn how a trusty notebook can help you focus, create, and - very important - not forget.

Comment below a tool or hack that helps you be productive!📒

node.title: Basics of Bossing Up Ep. 62: Notebooks

node.text:
🔥Oh snap, what do I do when I don’t know what to do?🔥

Here’s the deal: most of us find ourselves asking these kinds of questions often. Today, I’m giving you the answers!
⚡️Review - create some self awareness, observe your natural behavior and how it makes you feel. 
⚡️Read - lean into your resources and diversify content consumption. 
⚡️Reiterate - share what you’re experiencing and learning with your squad! 

What is a time when you didn’t know what to do, and what moves did you make to get through it?

node.title: Basics of Bossing Up Ep 61: What do you do when you don’t know what to do?

Today on #bbu we’re talking 🔥DMs🔥
Be honest- we’ve all slid into the dms at some point, but have you ever slipped into the dms? Maybe you have. 

Let’s talk about what that’s a problem. Luckily for you, I’m going to give you all the low down on how to slide into them for support, instead of slippinginto them in an non-constructive  manner. 

Comment below a supportive comment you want to see in your DMs 😉

node.text:
✨Instead of asking why me, ask why not me ✨

As women, we’re multidimensional people – we’re hard workers, friends, change-makers, mothers. I’m not just a one title person and I love owning that.

I’m honored to be the first woman featured in the new @adidaswomen series, Taking 5 With. Spent five minutes with the team talking about everything from my virtues to astrology to @lovesquad to @onepeloton. 🧡

I’ve put the link in bio if you want to read more. 🤩

So sometimes I do these fun impromptu fashion shows around @lovesquad newest apparel release. Yes, it’s a fashion show with no make up, no music and a whole lot of GREAT clothes! Not to mention some of my signature styling tips 😉

Thanks @fourthhousecreative @lovesquad for making clothes that make us all feel connected, and look good 🤩

Making memories 💍 welcome drinks have started…

WEDDING COUNTDOWN ⏰ 

🍾CALLING ALL Bride, Grooms, Partners, who are planning, had to postpone, about to say I do, want to wedding-reminisce, or wants this to be a hint to your partner. 
 *wink wink 😉 👀🤣*

👥Let’s drop it low and ride this milestone together in my 20min wedding celebration Barre (tonight) + 30min Wedding Celebration Ride (Thursday 8amET)!

All songs were sent in by you via my IG stories. So YOU created the PLAYLIST!!

Count yourself in & tag a workout buddy below ⬇️!!!!

node.text:
How do I do it all?? Truth be told…I don’t😂

✨That being said, I do have tips and tools to stay on top of what I have going on. 

✨Today on the Basics of Bossing Up, I’m going to tell you all about why a notebook (yes, that’s right, a pen and paper in 2021) helps me get it done!

✨Watch the full episode to learn how a trusty notebook can help you focus, create, and - very important - not forget.

Comment below a tool or hack that helps you be productive!📒
